        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 11 at 5:31PM EDT by NWS Peachtree City GA</headline>
        <description>At 531 PM EDT, a strong thunderstorm was near Kingston, or 11 miles
east of Rome, moving south at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Pea sized hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to exposed surfaces is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Kingston, Euharlee, Adairsville, and Cartersville.
</description>
        <instruction>People outdoors should seek shelter immediately.</instruction>
